:"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":5037,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/12\/prophet-dates-eid-al-fitr\/","url_meta":{"origin":5029,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Eid: The Prophet eats dates before Eid prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 12, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, would not proceed on the day of Eid al-Fitr\u00a0until he had eaten some dates. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 953 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Bukhari \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0633\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0645\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0650\u0643\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0643\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":8639,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/22\/fun-flexible-lenient-entertainment\/","url_meta":{"origin":5029,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Fun: So the Jews know there is leniency in Islam","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 22, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, placed my chin on his shoulder so I could watch\u00a0the Abyssin